name: Gemini 2.5 Computer Use Preview (Oct 2025)
description: Specialized model for building browser control agents. Built on Gemini 2.5 Pro's vision and reasoning, it can interact with UIs through screenshots, generating mouse clicks, keyboard inputs, and navigation actions.
notes: PREVIEW - Optimized for web browsers, capable of mobile UI control. Leading quality for browser control at lowest latency. Built-in safety training for misuse prevention. Pricing increases to $2.50/$15.00 per 1M tokens for prompts >200k. No free tier available.
